          <div style="position:absolute; bottom:24px; left:24px; right:24px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-end;">
            <div style="font-size:9px; font-weight:800; color:#cbd5e1; text-align:left; z-index:2;">스마트한 현장 관리<br>일잘러 앱</div>
            <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-end; gap:4px; z-index:2;">
